ivardefs.name: citation
ivardefs.desc: A bibliographic citation for the related artifact. This text SHOULD be formatted according to an accepted citation format.

ivardefs.name: display
ivardefs.desc: A brief description of the document or knowledge resource being referenced, suitable for display to a consumer.

ivardefs.name: document
ivardefs.desc: The document being referenced, represented as an attachment. This is exclusive with the resource element.

ivardefs.name: label
ivardefs.desc: A short label that can be used to reference the citation from elsewhere in the containing artifact, such as a footnote index.

ivardefs.name: resource
ivardefs.desc: The related resource, such as a library, value set, profile, or other knowledge resource.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The type of relationship to the related artifact.

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: A url for the artifact that can be followed to access the actual content.

properties.desc: Base StructureDefinition for RelatedArtifact Type: Related artifacts such as additional documentation, justification, or bibliographic references.
